Here are the details for our #TDSHolidayEscapade2020 #THE in short! ♥️ ⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Keep your child preoccupied with new skills, intact with DANCE and keep their creativity going during this period of Local School Holidays! #CircuitBreakerSG⠀⠀
⠀⠀
We have the following activities planned out for your child/ children to tide them through this School Holiday with lots of joy, love and DANCE!! 💃🏻♥️⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Week 1: 8 May, How to do your Ballet Bun 🙆🏻‍♀️⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Week 2: 15 May, DIY Muscle Roller and Exercises to release muscle tensions 💪🏼⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Week 3: 22 May, Decorate your old ballet shoes / pointe shoes 👩🏻‍🎨⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Week 4: FREE TRIAL lessons for all! For public as well!! 💃🏻 (25 - 28 May 2020) ⠀⠀
⠀⠀
We are very excited to share the details for our FREE TRIAL lessons for all with you!! ♥️ stay tuned we will reveal the details soon! ⠀⠀
⠀
